 <refentry id="function.apache-lookup-uri">
  <refnamediv>
   <refname>apache_lookup_uri</refname>
   <refpurpose>
    Effectue une requ&ecirc;te partielle pour l'URI sp&eacute;cifi&eacute;e
    et renvoie toutes les informations.
   </refpurpose>
  </refnamediv>
  <refsect1>
   <title>Description</title>
    <methodsynopsis>
     <type>object</type><methodname>apache_lookup_uri</methodname>
     <methodparam><type>string</type><parameter>filename</parameter></methodparam>
    </methodsynopsis>
   <para>
    <function>apache_lookup_uri</function> effectue une requ&ecirc;te partielle
    pour l'URI sp&eacute;cifi&eacute;e. Cette requ&ecirc;te permet de
    r&eacute;cup&eacute;rer toutes les informations importantes &agrave;
    propos de la ressource concern&eacute;e. Les propri&eacute;t&eacute;s
    de la classe renvoy&eacute;e sont les suivantes :
    <simplelist>
    <member><literal>status</literal></member>
    <member><literal>the_request</literal></member>
    <member><literal>status_line</literal></member>
    <member><literal>method</literal></member>
    <member><literal>content_type</literal></member>
    <member><literal>handler</literal></member>
    <member><literal>uri</literal></member>
    <member><literal>filename</literal></member>
    <member><literal>path_info</literal></member>
    <member><literal>args</literal></member>
    <member><literal>boundary</literal></member>
    <member><literal>no_cache</literal></member>
    <member><literal>no_local_copy</literal></member>
    <member><literal>allowed</literal></member>
    <member><literal>send_bodyct</literal></member>
    <member><literal>bytes_sent</literal></member>
    <member><literal>byterange</literal></member>
    <member><literal>clength</literal></member>
    <member><literal>unparsed_uri</literal></member>
    <member><literal>mtime</literal></member>
    <member><literal>request_time</literal></member>
    </simplelist>
   </para>
   <note>
    <simpara>
     <function>apache_lookup_uri</function> ne fonctionne que lorsque &php; est
     install&eacute; sous la forme d'un module Apache.
    </simpara>
   </note>
  </refsect1>
 </refentry>

